CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 31, 1946 reads: "Barbour-Jones Nuptials...Wed at St. James Mr. and Mrs. Isaiah Jones Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Isaiah Jones Jr. wearing tuxedo with tails, and bride Betty Barbour Jones, wearing gown with long sleeves, tulle overlay, and veil with headpiece, standing in front of crushed velvet curtain
